msgstr ""
"Se produsentens spesifikasjoner for loddemaskeekspansjon, brobredde og "
"klaringsinnstillinger."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:33
msgid ""
"If no specifications are provided, setting these values to zero is "
"recommended."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ingen spesifikasjoner er gitt, anbefales det å sette disse verdiene til "
"null."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:46
msgid "Solder Mask Settings"
msgstr "Innstillinger for loddemaske"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:62
#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:67
msgid ""
"Global clearance between pads and the solder mask.\n"
"This value can be superseded by local values for a footprint or a pad.\n"
"Positive clearance means a solder mask opening bigger than the pad (typical "
"for solder mask clearance)."
msgstr ""
"Global klaring mellom pader og loddemaske.\n"
"Denne verdien kan overstyres av lokale verdier for et fotavtrykk eller en "
"pad.\n"
"Positiv klaring betyr en loddemaskeåpning som er større enn paden (typisk "
"for loddemaske-klaring)."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:75
msgid "Solder mask minimum web width:"
msgstr "Loddemaske minimum brobredde:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:77
#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:82
msgid ""
"Minimum distance between openings in the solder mask.\n"
"Pad openings closer than this distance will be plotted as a single opening."
msgstr ""
"Minimum avstand mellom åpninger i loddemasken.\n"
"Padåpninger nærmere enn denne avstanden vil bli plottet som en enkelt åpning."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:90
msgid "Solder mask to copper clearance:"
msgstr "Klaring mellom loddemaske og kobber:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:92
#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:97
msgid ""
"Minimum distance between a solder mask opening and a copper item with a "
"different net than the solder mask opening's parent.\n"
"Distances smaller than this minimum will create a DRC error."
msgstr ""
"Minimum avstand mellom en loddemaskeåpning og et kobberelement med et annet "
"nett enn loddemaskeåpningens overordnede.\n"
"Avstander mindre enn dette minimumet vil opprette en DRC-feil."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:105
msgid "Allow bridged solder mask apertures between pads within footprints"
msgstr "Tillat brodannende loddemaskeåpninger mellom pader innen fotavtrykk"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:106
msgid ""
"Disable DRC error checking for solder mask aperture bridging between pads in "
"the same footprint."
msgstr ""
"Deaktiver DRC-feilkontroll for brodannelse av loddemaskeåpninger mellom "
"pader i samme fotavtrykk."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:113
msgid "Tent vias:"
msgstr "Telt viaer:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:118
#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:123
msgid ""
"Tented: vias are covered with solder mask.\n"
"Not tented: vias are not covered with solder mask."
msgstr ""
"Teltet: viaer dekkes med loddemaske.\n"
"Ikke teltet: viaer dekkes ikke med loddemaske."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:136
msgid "Solder Paste Settings"
msgstr "Innstillinger for loddepasta"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:167
#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:172
msgid ""
"Global clearance ratio between pads and the solder paste as a percentage of "
"the pad size.\n"
"A value of 10 means the clearance value is 10 percent of the pad size.\n"
"This value can be superseded by local values for a footprint or a pad.\n"
"Final clearance value is the sum of this value and the absolute clearance "
"value."
msgstr ""
"Globalt klaringsforhold i prosent mellom pader og loddepasta.\n"
"En verdi på 10 betyr at klaringsverdien er 10 prosent av padstørrelsen.\n"
"Denne verdien kan overstyres av lokale verdier for et fotavtrykk eller en "
"pad.\n"
"Endelig klaringsverdi er summen av denne verdien og den absolutte "
"klaringsverdien."

